OK, #narcolepsyfamily, more #Nchat items follow. Just got out of meeting on 'Clinical Decision Making in #Narcolepsy Management' #Sleep2014
At this talk were Drs. Thorpy, Mignot, Pelayo, Perking, and Swick. Had overview of #narcolepsy diagnosis and treatment, then cases. #Nchat
Dr. Mignot noted that the autoimmunity in #narcolepsy seems to be T-cell mediated. In future, a blood test may be used to diagnose. #Nchat
Dr. Thorpy noted sodium oxybate (#Xyrem) is first line treatment of #narcolepsy / #cataplexy. Armodafinil (Nuvigil) may help EDS. #Nchat
Dr. Thorpy noted that in Europe the histaminergic H3 antagonist/inverse agonist #pitolisant is used for #narcolepsy. #Nchat
A panel discussion question dealt with meds for #narcolepsy during pregnancy. All 5 panelists noted no specific contraindications. #Nchat
Dr. Mignot tells pregnant pts with #narcolepsy that whether to use meds depends on their degree of guilt if negative impact on baby. #Nchat
Dr. Mignot and Swick noted that they have had a total of 12 patients on #Xyrem for #narcolepsy deliver normal babies. Anecdotal. #Nchat
